DeathSteel::

He flew down towards the predacon base. He landed just outside the 
shields and transformed into bot mode. He opened his comm 
link. "Greetings to you. I am DeathSteel. Newly arrived to this 
planet. Since you are close to my shuttle landing, I wish to speak to 
you. I have checked your signatures and it shows that you are the 
same as I, a predacon. Allow me entrance and so I may speak to the 
leader here."  He then stood there and waited. He kept his sences 
sharp in case this backfired.
